## EXECUTION SEQUENCE SUMMARY

```
PHASE 0: Setup (run once)
  0.1 list_companies
  0.2 lookup_asin_catalog
  0.3 list_ryg_thresholds
       │
PHASE 1: Market Data (parallel where possible)
  ├── 1.1 analyze_search_query_performance
  ├── 1.2 analyze_search_catalog_performance
  ├── 1.4 get_search_term_momentum
  ├── 1.5 get_competitive_landscape
  └── 1.6 get_conversion_leak_analysis
       │
  1.3 get_keyword_funnel_metrics  ← depends on 1.1 output (specific keywords)
       │
PHASE 2: Advertising Data (parallel)
  ├── 2.1 analyze_search_terms
  ├── 2.2 analyze_campaign_performance
  └── 2.3 get_cross_sell_opportunities
       │
PHASE 3: Operations (parallel)
  ├── 3.1 get_inventory_landed_cost
  ├── 3.2 analyze_fifo_cogs
  ├── 3.3 analyze_profit_and_loss
  ├── 3.4 list_stock_replenishment_risk_items
  ├── 3.5 list_fba_replenishment_candidates
  ├── 3.6 analyze_sales_velocity
  ├── 3.7 list_product_logistics_parameters
  ├── 3.8 list_po_placement_candidates
  └── 3.9 shipment_arrival_oracle
       │
PHASE 4: Synthesis (sequential)
  4.1 generate_sales_forecast
  4.2 analyze_repeat_purchases
  4.3 list_reports → get_report_details
       │
  ▼ OUTPUT: Complete Growth Machine Dossier
```

