## DEPENDENCY GRAPH

```
list_companies ──→ lookup_asin_catalog ──┬──→ PHASE 1 (all)
                                          ├──→ PHASE 2 (all)
                                          └──→ PHASE 3 (all)

PHASE 1.1 (SQP) ──→ 1.3 (keyword funnel — needs specific keywords from SQP)

PHASE 1 + PHASE 2 ──→ CROSS-REFERENCE for:
  • Keyword Gap Report (SQP keywords missing from PPC)
  • Incrementality Matrix (SQP share vs PPC attributed clicks)
  • Blue Ocean List (SQP high-volume + PPC zero-spend)

PHASE 3.1 (landed cost) + 3.3 (P&L) ──→ True Contribution Margin
PHASE 3.4 (risk items) + 3.6 (velocity) ──→ Marketing Throttle Mode
PHASE 3.7 (lead times) + 3.4 (stockout risk) ──→ Last Launch Date
```

---

## NOTES

- **All tools require `company_id`** — get it from Step 0.1 first.
- **Most brand analytics tools require ASIN(s)** — get from Step 0.2.
- **Advertising tools require `profile_id`** — may need `list_selling_partner_accounts` or similar.
- **Phase 1 and Phase 2 are independent** — can run in parallel.
- **Phase 3 is independent of Phases 1 and 2** — all three phases can run in parallel after Phase 0.
- **Phase 4 (synthesis) depends on all prior phases** — run last.
- **The cross-referencing (Gap, Incrementality, Blue Ocean) is done by the AI agent** in post-processing, not by individual tools.